      "text": [
        "1187 - وَقَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «مَنْ صَلَّى بِقَوْمٍ فَاخْتَصَّ نَفْسَهُ بِالدُّعَاءِ دُونَهُمْ فَقَدْ خَانَهُمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1187 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said: \"Whoever leads a group in prayer and reserves the supplication for himself, excluding them, has betrayed them”."
        ]
      }
    },
